請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n今後呂布軍&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9xT9nv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9xT9nv7.jpg&h=1f0c60d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另特別感謝眾軍師無私奉獻及回贈股息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d72ec4e9fd1c31650c557808a4c0a47ad4a66cc","tid":2438972,"uid":28558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T02:06:01.000Z","msg":"GME琴晚明明大暴升做乜賺咗咁少"},{"pid":"59a833dd9039b2a262915dbd87acd5f3de6c8b0b","tid":2438972,"uid":99885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"師兄 你膠又膠唔哂 仲有啲型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e828257cdbcdf31d5207b3c7c2f132d167b1ea52","tid":2438972,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b538d679c01b2899fe5982f62a6bb0c7ecc6639","tid":2438972,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T02:05:01.000Z","msg":"「連燈力」基金 第七次股東大會操作結算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNtQRmS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNtQRmS.png&h=624525fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fe3tC1S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFe3tC1S.png&h=38a6305e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74ydO8x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74ydO8x.png&h=fdfb3f16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總成本1018.1 HP 剩餘<span class=\"green\">891.6</span> HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">10.84%</span><br />\n「連燈力」基金 第八波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」呂布軍成立只為了股東日日有燒賣食，此夢想，已踏出關鍵一步。<br />\n<br />\n1. 本次操作為ALL IN制， 收集此帖巴打主流意見<br />\n2. 第八波操作買入軍師兵士們主流意見之股票<br />\n3. 第八波買入時間預計約為<span class=\"red\">盤前17:00</span><br />\n4. 第八波買入選擇為盤前乞<br />\n5. 第七波賣出時機分為&darr;<br />\na. 到達預計賣出時間<span class=\"red\">盤前22:00</span>或保留至下一階段<br />\nb. 增幅到達7%將立即設下5%止蝕位保存勝仗<br />\nc. 10%止賺及止蝕位<br />\n6. 若結算資金增長5% 隨機向選中買入股票巴打派發Payme燒賣一串<